    {
      "text": "Last edit almost 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n92\nNeeds Review\n92\nC-175 we know nothing about. Without this contrast we suppose traces of God in, say. design + purpose, but this is inference + speculation, + the Gnostic knows this because he knows - or knows of - the real thing: deity indubitably palpable in world, absolutely unmistakable + vivid. The explanations given by the Gnostics for this are blatant absurdities because of their drastic error in supposing literal space + literal spatial Fall",
